comment: Hill (IND) maintains a legal guarding position on the play to the basket by Duncan (SAS).

Turner (IND) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding. Turner's contact with Aldridge's arm does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound but it does cause the incidental contact to his face.
Turner (IND) sets the screen on Mills (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Aldridge (SAS) cleanly strips the ball from Ellis (IND) on his drive to the basket.
Duncan (SAS) sets the screen on Ellis (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Hill (IND) and Duncan (SAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Hill (IND) makes contact with Mills (SAS) that affects his RSBQ.
Hill (IND) and Leonard (SAS) briefly engage and separate following the defensive switch.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Green (SAS) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
Green (SAS) makes incidental contact with Ellis (IND) as he defends near midcourt.
Green (SAS) makes incidental contact with Ellis (IND) that does not affect his RSBQ.
George (IND) makes incidental contact with Leonard (SAS) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Duncan (SAS) sets the screen on George (IND) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Leonard (SAS) makes contact with George's (IND) arm on his layup attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) commits a take foul on Hill (IND).
